/span><span>∞</span></span></span></span></span> の範囲で時間積分したものである。</p>\n<p>角周波数<span><span><span>ω\\omega</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>ω</span></span></span></span></span>の関数<span><span><span>F(ω)F(\\omega)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>F</span><span>(</span><span>ω</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span> で表せることになる。</p>\n<h2>フーリエ逆変換</h2>\n<p>角周波数<span><span><span>ω\\omega</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>ω</span></span></span></span></span>の関数<span><span><span>F(ω)F(\\omega)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>F</span><span>(</span><span>ω</span><span>)</span></span></span></span></span>を時間<span><span><span>tt</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>t</span></span></span></span></span>の関数で表す。</p>\n<div><span><span><span>f(t)=12π∫−∞∞F(ω)ejωtdωf(t) = \\frac{1}{2\\pi}\\int_{-\\infty}^\\infty F(\\omega) e^{j\\omega t} d\\omega</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\"><span><span></span><span>f</span><span>(</span><span>t</span><span>)</span><span></span><span>=</span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span>2</span><span>π</span></span></span><span><span></span><span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>1</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></span><span></span><span><span>∫</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>−</span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span><span></span><span><span>∞</span></span></span></span><span>​</span></span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span><span>F</span><span>(</span><span>ω</span><span>)</span><span><span>e</span><span><span><span><span><span><span></span><span><span><span>j</span><span>ω</span><span>t</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>d</span><span>ω</span></span></s